sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Free User
    participant FE as React<br/>BlockedIPsPage
    participant API1 as DRF<br/>BlockedIPListView
    participant API2 as DRF<br/>UnblockIPByIdView
    participant SER as BlockedIPSerializer
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Navigate to Blocked IPs page
    FE->>API1: GET /api/blocked-ips/
    API1->>DB: BlockedIP.objects.all()
    DB-->>API1: QuerySet[BlockedIP]
    API1->>SER: BlockedIPSerializer(ips, many=True)
    API1-->>FE: 200 OK {blocked_ips: [...]}
    FE-->>U: Display blocked IPs table
    U->>FE: Click "Unblock" on blocked IP
    FE->>API2: POST /api/blocked-ips/{id}/unblock/
    API2->>DB: BlockedIP.objects.get(pk=id).delete()
    DB-->>API2: Deleted
    API2-->>FE: 200 OK "IP unblocked"
    FE-->>U: IP removed from blocked list
